Help Type: topic
Topic: command

Command Overview

Object commands:
  wikigraph search <archive-or-scope-uri> <query>
  wikigraph list <archive-or-scope-uri>
  wikigraph get <object-uri>
  wikigraph related <object-uri>
  wikigraph evidence <object-uri>
  wikigraph pack <object-uri>

URI routing:
  Read `wikigraph help uri` before using object commands.

Archive commands:
  wikigraph create <archive.sdpub>
  wikigraph export <archive.sdpub>
  wikigraph estimate <archive.sdpub>
  wikigraph index <archive.sdpub>
  wikigraph transform [options]

Generation:
  wikigraph queue add <archive.sdpub> --chapter <id> --task <reading-graph|reading-summary|knowledge-graph> --accept-cost

Maintenance:
  wikigraph meta <archive.sdpub>
  wikigraph cover <archive.sdpub>
  wikigraph chapter <action> <archive.sdpub>
  wikigraph config status
